### Создать команду (ROLE_CLUB)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Team 2015",
  "year": 2015,
  "description": "Команда 2015 года рождения"
}

### Получить список команд клуба с пагинацией (ROLE_CLUB, ROLE_CLUB_METHODIST, ROLE_COACH, ROLE_MAIN_COACH)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams?page=0&size=18
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить команду по ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Обновить команду (ROLE_CLUB)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Team 2016",
  "year": 2016,
  "description": "Обновлённое описание"
}

### Деактивировать команду (ROLE_CLUB)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/active?active=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Активировать команду (ROLE_CLUB)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/active?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Загрузить логотип команды (ROLE_CLUB)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="team-logo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-logo.png
--boundary--

### Получить логотип команды
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/logo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить список тренеров команды (ROLE_CLUB, ROLE_CLUB_METHODIST)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/coaches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Назначить тренера команде (ROLE_CLUB)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/coaches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

### Убрать тренера из команды (ROLE_CLUB)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clubs/{{clubId}}/teams/{{teamId}}/coaches/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}